rules.name: Wireless Block List Default
rules.conditions_formatted: Radius.NAS-Port-Type equals Wireless - IEEE 802.11 AND IdentityGroup.Name equals Endpoint Identity Groups:Blocked List

rules.name: Profiled Cisco IP Phones
rules.conditions_formatted: IdentityGroup.Name equals Endpoint Identity Groups:Profiled:Cisco-IP-Phone

rules.name: Profiled Non Cisco IP Phones
rules.conditions_formatted: EndPoints.LogicalProfile equals IP-Phones

rules.name: Unknown_Compliance_Redirect
rules.conditions_formatted: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals Unknown

rules.name: NonCompliant_Devices_Redirect
rules.conditions_formatted: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals NonCompliant

rules.name: Compliant_Devices_Access
rules.conditions_formatted: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals Compliant

rules.name: Employee_EAP-TLS
rules.conditions_formatted: Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals Wireless802_1x AND EndPoints.BYODRegistration equals Yes AND Network Access.EapAuthentication equals EAP-TLS AND CERTIFICATE.Subject Alternative Name equals Calling-Station-ID

rules.name: Employee_Onboarding
rules.conditions_formatted: Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals Wireless802_1x AND Network Access.EapAuthentication equals EAP-MSCHAPv2

rules.name: Wi-Fi_Guest_Access
rules.conditions_formatted: Network Access.UseCase equals Guest Flow AND Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals WirelessMAB

rules.name: Wi-Fi_Redirect_to_Guest_Login
rules.conditions_formatted: Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals WirelessMAB

rules.name: Basic_Authenticated_Access
rules.conditions_formatted: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed
